Reference

All functions

get_adref()

return handle to anndata

get_dsref()

return handle to huggingface datasets module

get_gf_python()

use import_from_python in reticulate to get the geneformer modules

get_gf_safetensors()

retrieve or place the model.safetensors for Geneformer (6L?) in cache, zipped

get_panc_loom_path()

retrieve or place a loom file for Grun/Muraro's pancreas study in BiocFileCache

get_panc_tok_path()

retrieve or place a zipfile with tokenization dataset for Grun/Muraro's pancreas study in BiocFileCache

get_safet()

expose safetensors infrastructure

getgf()

tickle basilisk installation

gf_tokenize_h5ad()

tokenize a h5ad file

gf_tokenize_loom()

tokenize a loom file

nwts_safet()

count number of weights in safetensors file

panc_loom_url()

give URL for 'loom' file for pancreas data

panc_tok_zip_url()

give URL for 'dataset' corresponding to tokenization of pancreas data

setup_and_run_Classifier()

returns instance of geneformer.Classifier

usebert()

work with a template python script to illustrate mask substitution by a BERT model

usebert_pipeline()

work with a template python script to illustrate mask substitution by a BERT model, and use the pipeline unmasker to produce a list of scored substitutions
